name: Edge TV (3:39) digital video 720 X 480, stereo
description: Animal Charm created this video for Light Industry's screening on 10/14/2008, CROSSROADS: tribute to Bruce Conner. It was released on Cinemad's Almanac 2009 anthology DVD and is the prequel to "All Night Water"- a 2 CH vid piece in the Hammer Museum's Made In LA 2012 exhibition.
